{"tid":1946183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"竹篙灣檢疫中心單野真係好撚癲 2億起黎隔離人","createTime":"2020-03-27T12:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T12:43:49.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c4b902b7629d8de656ec92889598517852a5a8","tid":1946183,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，政府在大嶼山竹篙灣一直預留60公頃填海土地，供香港迪士尼樂園發展第二期，惟該地已閒置多年。政府早前指會於該土地興建檢疫中心，首階段建100個單位，連同工地平整及基礎設施共花費1.9億元。<span style=\"color: red;\">首批單位預計5月落成啟用</span>。竹篙灣檢疫中心第二期則料興建500個檢疫單位，工程預計於今年4月開始，並於7月完成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n190萬一間貨櫃屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d38ae9f89dc304e7d8b781589910412d6b8a90","tid":1946183,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"190萬夠起一棟三層村屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220c4ae36f2ad42a78ed0ba87217e25519633a6c","tid":1946183,"uid":13433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:35:01.000Z","msg":"其實係幫迪士尼填平塊地 <br />\n等第時唔洗用咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3f623a024b5bba3a23c52c0d6a05d284c90c3b","tid":1946183,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/YpUNzi5_RNHdNJV_sDyJOuFa-7LpgDKGvuOR_ydkJHejuSFqcYkIeTGO-cd6mi4p_z7eQBQ2fw7oIzJYIzfRDV0miJMoxoGF_h6MId9BxyZZG6HyF2eoSm2C2vA6vw2DYdZO-SWYjv-AbgUXfRk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FYpUNzi5_RNHdNJV_sDyJOuFa-7LpgDKGvuOR_ydkJHejuSFqcYkIeTGO-cd6mi4p_z7eQBQ2fw7oIzJYIzfRDV0miJMoxoGF_h6MId9BxyZZG6HyF2eoSm2C2vA6vw2DYdZO-SWYjv-AbgUXfRk&h=d1a763c7&s={S